Melville in Johannesburg in Johannesburg is again flying the SA flag high, with 7th Street showing up at number 12 on the coolest streets in the world. eNCA's senior reporter Aviwe Mtila checked out what makes it so cool. #DStv403 #eNCA JOHANNESBURG - Johannesburg's Melville is again flying the South African flag high. The popular 7th Street ranked 12th on a list of the coolest streets in the world, according to a survey by Time Out magazine. Over 27,000 participants previously rated Melville among the world's 40 coolest neighbourhoods last year. Watch eNCA's senior reporter Aviwe Mtila explore Melville a little further in the video above.